{"tid":2329430,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[巫師3 求指點] 錯過左百果園任務+昆特牌","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T11:05:04.000Z","uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"60127b249813d2ad41584616389079ee898d4f78","tid":2329430,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"玩緊一周目, 玩到威倫, 15lvl 左右<br />\n<br />\n係百果園個陣<br />\n1. 冇玩昆特牌, 去到威倫先識玩<br />\n2. 因為冇錢, 所以冇買昆特牌<br />\n3. 冇玩賽馬, 覺得晒時間<br />\n4. 冇解晒d 支線, 獵魔任務<br />\n5. 未搵齊6 個魔力之所<br />\n<br />\n去到威倫<br />\n血腥男爵已經帶左個女去醫病<br />\n但原來未同佢玩昆特牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n使唔使重玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c654d518f5b7daa4de6ca66960ea81acd877a771","tid":2329430,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5ba2a26f409570e1a4c4be83ca707519bdf09a","tid":2329430,"uid":367364,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RxD9AmY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRxD9AmY.png&h=f8ce0789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收嗲啦石頭佬 原始人有電腦玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e90de3a01d7b0cf8eaf26750dbc7022afeda405","tid":2329430,"uid":377064,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"冇錢咪用石頭買咯"},{"pid":"011fb12303d6aef76966e8ff0b3137c71c819264","tid":2329430,"uid":301989,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"石頭仔你都有玩？<br />\n好撚悶喎隻game <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=